  <md:title>Graph with Intercepts</md:title>
  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para>
<list>
<item>Identify the <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math>- and <m:math><m:mi>y</m:mi></m:math>- intercepts on a graph</item>
<item>Find the <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math>-  and <m:math><m:mi>y</m:mi></m:math>- intercepts from an equation of a line</item>
<item>Graph a line using the intercepts</item>
</list></md:abstract>
